      "versionNonce": 1388002550,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775584788067,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The weighting of the graph should be\ndetermined by the wishes of the user.\nSomething like:\n- Less walk\n- Less transfers\n- Less time\n\nEven better if we serialize this\ninformation on the graph and then run\nthe path-finding algorithm with dynamic\nuser preferences.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "CgoDIDLbdabCsJteo6z5F",
      "originalText": "The weighting of the graph should be determined by the wishes of the user. Something like:\n- Less walk\n- Less transfers\n- Less time\n\nEven better if we serialize this information on the graph and then run the path-finding algorithm with dynamic user preferences.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
